{"tid":653190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃洋達: 熱血時報就係保衛粵語既最前線, 如果想保衛粵語就買熱血時報既產品同課金","createTime":"2018-05-04T13:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T11:38:50.000Z","uid":157483,"like":14,"dislike":118,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"b792e5d64fd6ea1ba77412eb6279ea4196dc6aad","tid":653190,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:20:02.000Z","msg":"熱血政治 5/3 內容<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/83/1173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fprog%2F83%2F1173&d=%2FuKJaaJ4W3EtDts%2FqpNOQy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=2bee9128\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/83/1173</a><br />\n<br />\n黃洋達: <br />\n「一直進行文化抗爭既熱血時報，就係保衛粵語既最前線，我地就係代表保衛粵語」<br />\n<br />\n「好多人都有保衛粵語既心，但佢地唔識創作丫嘛，好多人識創作 但冇保衛粵語既心，而我地咪就係兩者兼備囉，你睇下陳奕迅而家都唔出粵語歌啦，而我地一路都堅持粵語創作，所以咪要買我地唱片囉，１００蚊有２１首歌，一首歌５蚊都唔洗，幾撚抵！」<br />\n<br />\n「所以課金啦！課金比我地就等於支持粵語，幫手貼條課金ｌｉｎｋ落ｃｈａｔｒｏｏｍ」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/uZB87v1iAmA/mqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FuZB87v1iAmA%2Fmqdefault.jpg&h=bbf9bbdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33af128d534e2d09a9169969f25d1cc2ec523011","tid":653190,"uid":5843,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:25:40.000Z","msg":"收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcd43e6d0bd8f0b9f6296ffeacdbb0e56b3f23c","tid":653190,"uid":45285,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:26:47.000Z","msg":"同乞兒有乜分別。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c960f643303155ebd2583bd3f7440d165af8ef90","tid":653190,"uid":122233,"like":8,"dislike":13,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:27:14.000Z","msg":"咁有心 即課10000 唔夠再課"},{"pid":"aafa9961560b676093227e3396c2d8719e55c5c7","tid":653190,"uid":65128,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:29:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pi